---
title: Mediterranean Couscous Bowls with Hummus, Cucumber Salad, & Lemon Cream
description: Hummus: not just for pita chips anymore! This versatile dip is the perfect topper for these Mediterranean power bowls. Here, it’s mixed with smoky paprika for a delicious flavor boost. In case you were wondering, underneath the hummus lies a whole world of deliciousness. At the base, there’s fluffy, Turkish-spiced couscous mixed with lemon zest. On top, you’ve also got cucumber-dill salad, roasted bell pepper and tomato, creamy lemon sauce, and crumbly feta cheese. Together, it’s a multi-layered melange that’ll knock your chickpea-loving socks off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-hummus-couscous-bowls-9aa1b9c2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mediterranean-hummus-couscous-bowls-5dcb270d75717c39e2461100-8037ffc6.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mediterranean-hummus-couscous-bowls-5dcb270d75717c39e2461100
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 580 kcal
  fat: 31 g
  saturated fat: 13 g
  carbohydrates: 60 g
  sugar: 9 g
